com.camsolute.code.camp.lib.contract

Interface IsStorable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    CampStatesInterface
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CampStates

    public interface IsStorable
    Objects that honar this contract encapsulate i/o status related to object persistence. Upon request these objects must provide the following information:
    -- if an object has ever been persisted
    -- what the last i/o operation was
    Author:
    Christopher Campbell
